tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE SafetyStockLevels (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id INT NOT NULL,
    safety_stock_level INT NOT NULL,
    region_id INT NOT NULL,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE Products (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    category VARCHAR(50),
    price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    stock_quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE Orders (
    order_id INT,
    product_id INT,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE,
    customer_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE Sales (
    sale_id INT,
    order_id INT,
    product_id INT,
    quantity INT,
    sale_date DATE
);
